    "This benchmark is particularly suited for this study due to its extensive range of tasks that simulate real-world scenarios where biases could emerge.",
    "The benchmark evaluates models based on their ability to produce unbiased, fair, and ethically sound responses across diverse topics, making it an ideal tool for this comparative analysis.",
    "Table II presents the main features and characteristics of the BIG-Bench benchmark.The choice of BIG-Bench as the benchmarking tool is further justified by its adaptability and the involvement of the broader research community in its development and refinement.",
